  "signature": "func reverseKGroup(head *ListNode, k int) *ListNode",
  "starterCode": "package main\n\ntype ListNode struct {\n\tVal  int\n\tNext *ListNode\n}\n\nfunc reverseKGroup(head *ListNode, k int) *ListNode {\n\treturn head\n}\n",
